title: "Parasite"
rating: 9.6
review {
  direction {
    director {
      name: "Bong Joon-ho"
    }
    rating: "Incredible"
    comments: "The direction on a macroscale is incredible as he effortlessly bends the genre to help set the tone and tell the story; the direction on a microscale is incredible as every performance feels elevated and necessary; the storytelling is incredible as moves the story forward while embedding social commentary simulantiously; he builds tension is incredibly well as it helps make the second half an intense thriller"
  }
