  }
  pacing: "Pacing is right as the movie moves and does not really feel like it is too slow or fast in any way"
  climax: "Climax is incredibly well executed as it feels like a we are finally reaching the boiling point for all of these chracters"
  tone: "Tone is very genre-bending, but at the end of the day is a 'black comedy-thriller' based on how the two halves of the movie are structured"
  final_notes: ""
  overall: "Overall, an incredible film that is truly genre-bending as Bong Joon-ho creates a timeless art-piece that is near perfect and is profound social commentary on class dynamics"
